name: Player
sql:
CREATE TABLE Player
(
	ID integer not null
		constraint Player_pk
			primary key autoincrement,
	username varchar(24) not null,
	password varchar(24) default "GabelstaplerGames" not null
, scoreBalance int default 0)

name: Items
sql:
CREATE TABLE Items
(
	ID integer not null
		constraint Items_pk
			primary key autoincrement,
	name varchar(24) not null,
	price int not null
)

name: Inventory
sql:
CREATE TABLE "Inventory"
(
	stock int default 0 not null,
	playerID int not null
		references Player,
	itemID int not null
		references Items,
	constraint Inventory_pk
		primary key (playerID, itemID)
)
